{"tid":1923300,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"DC鋼骨原來係「參考」Marvel既Deathlok","createTime":"2020-03-13T03:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T12:16:38.000Z","uid":105567,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7f68cbf058a333fd0743cd7606ec4ecc2c90f12e","tid":1923300,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T03:55:03.000Z","msg":"互相「參考」，參來參去<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Cyborg</strong> is a fictional superhero appearing in American comic books published by DC Comics. The character was created by writer Marv Wolfman and artist George P&eacute;rez and first appears in a special insert in DC Comics Presents #26 (October 1980).<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.dccomics.com/sites/default/files/imce/2018/08-AUG/Cyborg_v01_r01_5b6c7d7bef1616.90753062.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dccomics.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimce%2F2018%2F08-AUG%2FCyborg_v01_r01_5b6c7d7bef1616.90753062.jpg&h=f247456d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Deathlok </strong>(also referred to as Deathlok the Demolisher) is a fictional character appearing in American comic books published by Marvel Comics. He first appeared in Astonishing Tales #25 (Aug. 1974), created by Rich Buckler and Doug Moench. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://isteam.wsimg.com/ip/b014861c-740b-11e4-a962-14feb5d9f2e6/ols/5554_original/:/rs=w:600,h:600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fisteam.wsimg.com%2Fip%2Fb014861c-740b-11e4-a962-14feb5d9f2e6%2Fols%2F5554_original%2F%3A%2Frs%3Dw%3A600%2Ch%3A600&h=824af583&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a18f0cc7784af26a7eed85b7ca01a1c1bf786755","tid":1923300,"uid":3976,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T04:11:03.000Z","msg":"marvel dc果個年代好似好多都係互抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a10f49fd27c4f33f06d269cf0a551a2bd225aa4","tid":1923300,"uid":236891,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2